@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title CourierFlow - Physical DFD Level 0

rectangle "Customer Device / Browser" as Customer #FFF2CC
rectangle "Courier Device / Browser" as Courier #FFF2CC
rectangle "Admin Device / Browser" as Admin #FFF2CC
rectangle "Khalti Payment Gateway" as Khalti #FCE5CD

rectangle "React Frontend SPA\nVite build + React Router\nsrc/Routes.jsx\nsrc/pages/*\nsrc/components/*" as Frontend #D9EAF7
database "Browser Storage\nlocalStorage\nsessionStorage" as BrowserStorage #F4F4F4

rectangle "PHP REST API\nbackend/public/index.php" as Api #D9EAF7
rectangle "Dispatch Engine\nbackend/Algorithms/AutoAssign.php" as DispatchEngine #D9EAF7
rectangle "Route Engine\nbackend/Algorithms/RouteOptimization.php" as RouteEngine #D9EAF7

database "MySQL Database\ncourier schema" as MySQL #F4F4F4
database "File Upload Storage\nbackend/public/uploads/\navatars, proofs, support" as FileStorage #F4F4F4

Customer <--> Frontend : booking, tracking,\nchat, dashboard use
Courier <--> Frontend : assignment, navigation,\nproof, live status use
Admin <--> Frontend : monitoring,\nmanagement, support use

Frontend <--> BrowserStorage : auth token, role,\ndrafts, nav state
Frontend <--> Api : HTTP JSON requests / responses

Api <--> DispatchEngine : auto-assign calls\nassignment result
Api <--> RouteEngine : route recommend,\nselect, reoptimize
Api <--> MySQL : SQL reads / writes
Api <--> FileStorage : upload / read avatar,\nproof, support images
Api <--> Khalti : payment initiate /\npayment verify

DispatchEngine <--> MySQL : couriers, vehicles,\nbranches, bookings
RouteEngine <--> MySQL : graph, route plans,\nbookings, fleet data

@enduml
